      <title>津巴布韦命名新体育部长来代替Kirsty Coventry</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/zimbabwe-names-new-sports-minister-to-replace-kirsty-coventry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦总统艾默森·曼南格瓦（Emmerson Mnangagwa）退休了军队指挥官，任命他为新体育部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/zimbabwe-names-new-sports-minister-to-replace-kirsty-coventry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 18:20:23 GMT</pubDate>
